title: Renovated 2 Bedroom Penthouse w/ Complimentary WiFi & NW Views!
posting_body: ['Coppins Well', '1000 Minor Ave., Seattle, WA, 98104', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 30', 'OR Text', '30', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', '99 Walkscore!', 'Centrally Located to EVERYTHING!', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1007 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Tap into life at Coppins Well, a highrise community in one of Seattles original residential neighborhoods.', 'Tap into the arts, the culture, wellness, all just steps from your front door.', 'With jaw-dropping views and apartment homes designed to make you feel at home, youre tapping into the most unforgettable address youve ever had.', 'Apart from the prime First Hill location, the community offers multiple amenities including a rooftop deck with spectacular views, vegetable garden, movie lounge, and community room complete with private temperature-controlled wine lockers.', 'The interior unit features include city views, spacious layouts, updated finishes, and additional storage options.', 'Features', '- Storage', '- Closet Walk-in', '- Appliances Stainless', 'Community Amenities', '- Internet', '- Svc Cable', '- Paid Cable', '- Granite Counters', '- Fitness Center', '- Business Center', '- Club House', '- On-site Maintenance', '- Flooring Hardwood', '- BBQ Grill', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday-Sunday: 10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Rent $50 | Deposit $300', 'Income Requirements:', '3x', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'OQXA3w3xJ']
